      "rationale": "Testing was performed under a single ASTM F1717 loading configuration. While laboratory environment and displacement rate were controlled and documented, only one test condition was evaluated. This limits achieved level to Gradation 2, below the required Gradation 3. This gap is acknowledged and accepted given the standardised nature of the F1717 protocol and the corroborating multi-laboratory data."
